    Add messaging components and hooks for boat chats
    
    Introduces a messaging system for boat bookings, including new components (ChatHeader, CustomerCaptainChat, MessageBubble, MessageInput, VirtualMessageList), related hooks (useBookingMessaging, useMessages), and supporting utilities. Updates dependencies and adds tests for messaging functionality. Also updates BoatCard, BookingForm, BoatListing, and imageUtils to integrate messaging features.

